room_title: Escape room "The Forgotten Library" by Escapades in Sioux Falls
room_address: 3313 S Western Ave Sioux Falls, SD 57105
room_description: Mr. Miller is a writer who lives outside a small town where he stays locked away writing in his library most of the time. The people in the town do not know him but refer to him as the writer. Soon people notice they have not seen him in over a month so a group of concerned towns folk goes to check on him, but end up locked in his library. Now they have 60 mins to get out before they are gassed!
